title: Ep. #102 | February Comebacks of 2021
description:
Hey! Let's catch up with each other. Eric is in LA, writing new music, and dealing with adult acne. Woo 30s! Also, 2021 in K-Pop is still in high gear with the latest set of comebacks this past February. We're talking SUNMI's "Tail (꼬리)", SHINee's "Don't Call Me", and GOT7's "Encore".
